[
  {
    "startTime": 10.054,
    "endTime": 11.557,
    "text": "So glad autumn is here!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.557,
    "endTime": 13.055,
    "text": "I know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.055,
    "endTime": 16.898,
    "text": "There's just something about autumn　that resonates with me as a person."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.898,
    "endTime": 18.556,
    "text": "Right, you like it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.556,
    "endTime": 23.556,
    "text": "But for me, it's something more!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.87,
    "endTime": 25.78,
    "text": "Not more than me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.78,
    "endTime": 32.455,
    "text": "See, I embrace the feeling of a frosty morning chill　fading in the afternoon sun!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.455,
    "endTime": 34.498,
    "text": "Right, a comfortable temperature."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.499,
    "endTime": 41.221000000000004,
    "text": "But, see, I love the fall because　I love the sound of dry leaves crackling underfoot!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.221,
    "endTime": 43.299,
    "text": "Oh, a universally beloved sound?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.299,
    "endTime": 44.054,
    "text": "Great."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.054,
    "endTime": 48.013000000000005,
    "text": "I love fall because of the hum of excitement　of a new school year!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.013,
    "endTime": 51.518,
    "text": "Oh, the thing children are required　by law to do?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.519,
    "endTime": 52.97,
    "text": "How special."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.97,
    "endTime": 58.856,
    "text": "See, I love autumn in a deeper way,　because I love the creamy, zesty taste　of pumpkin spice!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.856,
    "endTime": 61.353,
    "text": "- Oh, you mean Starbucks' most popular flavor?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.353,
    "endTime": 62.363,
    "text": "How unique."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.363,
    "endTime": 63.349,
    "text": "But for me-- - For you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.349,
    "endTime": 64.10499999999999,
    "text": "For me. For you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.114,
    "endTime": 64.614,
    "text": "For me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.614,
    "endTime": 65.196,
    "text": "For you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.196,
    "endTime": 68.925,
    "text": "I love the color bursting forth from every tree!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.926,
