    "text": "Oh, you mean thing that powers all of New England tourism?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.495,
    "endTime": 73.912,
    "text": "That's what you love?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.912,
    "endTime": 78.533,
    "text": "See, I'm a brooding mystery, because I love the macabre darkness of Halloween!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.533,
    "endTime": 83.339,
    "text": "Oh, you mean the closest thing modern Americans have to a bacchanalian orgy of delight?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.339,
    "endTime": 87.25,
    "text": "I've claimed ownership over the season, and no one else can love it more than I can!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.251,
    "endTime": 91.268,
    "text": "I can! I love the way the world looks when it's dappled in golden light!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.268,
    "endTime": 93.974,
    "text": "I love the sound of rain tapping against the window!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.974,
    "endTime": 96.922,
    "text": "I could smell cinnamon every day for the rest of my life!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.922,
